#id=1
#text=Upon the realization I was out of milk and had nothing to make for dinner , I decided to stop at the grocery store .
#id=2
#text=It was down the street from my apartment , so I hopped into my car and was there within minutes .
#id=3
#text=I grabbed a basket and headed to the back right corner to get some ground beef , then headed to the back left to grab some milk .
#id=4
#text=My journey then continued to the produce department where I snagged some broccoli and onions .
#id=5
#text=With my eyes fixed on the checkout line , I headed in that direction trying to keep my eyes away from the ice cream section .
#id=6
#text=I failed and took some chocolate ice cream , went to check out .
#id=7
#text=The line was long , my eyes then wandered to the tabloids while the line moved forward .
#id=8
#text=I put my products onto the conveyer belt and smiled at the check out lady .
#id=9
#text=After I typed in my phone number for a slight discount , I swung my purse around me to get my wallet and paid .
#text=I took my bags of stuff and walked to my car .
